perl-OpenGL
-------------------------------------------
Perl module to display 3D data using OpenGL, GLU, and GLUT.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.24-2
  libGL1-6.5.1-1
  libGLU1-6.5.1-1
  libX11_6-1.1.1-1
  libglut3-2.4.0-1
  perl-5.8.7-5

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding devel packages)
  cygwin-1.5.24-2
  binutils-20060817-1
  cygport-0.2.11-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-3
  make-3.81-1
  perl-5.8.7-5

Canonical homepage:
  http://search.cpan.org/~bfree/OpenGL/

Canonical download:
  http://www.cpan.org/authors/id/B/BF/BFREE/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack perl-OpenGL-0.55-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./perl-OpenGL-0.55-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/perl-OpenGL-0.55-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/perl-OpenGL-0.55-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

  /etc/postinstall/perl-OpenGL.sh
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.8/cygwin/OpenGL.pm
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.8/cygwin/auto/OpenGL/.packlist
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.8/cygwin/auto/OpenGL/OpenGL.bs
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.8/cygwin/auto/OpenGL/OpenGL.dll
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.8/cygwin/auto/OpenGL/autosplit.ix
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.8/cygwin/auto/OpenGL/libOpenGL.dll.a
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/perl-OpenGL-0.55.README
  /usr/share/doc/perl-OpenGL-0.55/COPYRIGHT
  /usr/share/doc/perl-OpenGL-0.55/Changes
  /usr/share/doc/perl-OpenGL-0.55/INSTALL
  /usr/share/doc/perl-OpenGL-0.55/README
  /usr/share/doc/perl-OpenGL-0.55/TODO
  /usr/share/perl/cygwin-pods/5.8/OpenGL.pod

